<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3650476>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Distribution map of Steindachnerina brevipinna in both rio Paraná and rio Paraguai (green), S. nigrotaenia in the rio Paraguai (red), and S. insculpta in the upper rio Paraná (yellow). Pentagons indicate type localities. Some symbols represent more than one collecting locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3650476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

